    GET STARTED    

















      Mobile Bidding & Auction Software Seamlessly manage all types of charity auctions including: silent auctions, live auctions and online auctions.    





  










				Mobilize your cause™.  Maximize your silent auction.			




				With BidPal Auction Software and Mobile Bidding you have choices. Whether you are looking for a fully staffed event or a Do-It-Yourself solution, our team provides you with options that will exceed your expectations and meet your budget.			













  












REQUEST A DEMO





				MOBILE BIDDING			



Mobile bidding is a revolutionary new paperless bidding method that allows participants to bid straight from their phones. Not only will your organization receive more bids through mobile bidding, but it can also help you simplify your event execution and management.



BidPal mobile bidding and auction software simplifies all aspects of your live and silent auction and adds an unparalleled level of fun and excitement to your events.



One size doesn’t fit all, and that’s why BidPal Charity Auction Software and Mobile Bidding offers a Do-It-Yourself solution as well as a Full Service packages that include onsite event and technical expertise.








SEE BIDPAL IN ACTION







 














  















				How mobile bidding works			








				01			




				Start early			



Manage auction item procurement. Publicize your charity auction, sell tickets online, promote sponsorships and let the bidding begin.




 





				02			




				Upon Arrival			



Registration like you’ve never seen it before. Seamlessly capture guest info, swipe credit cards for express checkout, and log guests in on their mobile phones.




 





				03			




				During the Event			



Experience unparalleled competitive bidding, text outbid notifications, raffle ticket purchases, sign-up parties, max bids, donation moments and more.




 





				04			




				Close Out			



Instantaneous checkout, emailed receipts, and robust post-event analytics and reporting results in happy guests, volunteers and staff.




 










  






























  



























  













				Auction Software Features
Designed for Fundraisers			












     PROCUREMENT & PACKAGING
Offering intuitive tools to help manage auction items.

Generate solicitation letters
Track procurement status
Log item location
Bundle multiple items into packages
Auto assign package numbers, starting bids and raises
Group items by category












     TICKETING
Sell tickets and manage RSVPs online.

Customizable ticket packages for donors & sponsors
Offer coupon codes for discounts
Sell VIP access, raffle tickets, and party passes
Collect seating requests and guest names’
Track guest dietary restrictions
Accept additional donations















     Online Auctions
Easily create unlimited online auctions allowing your donors to effortlessly bid anywhere.

Allow guests to preview auction packages
Jump start bidding prior to an event
Sell fixed price items
Showcase event countdown clock
Hold a post-event fire sale of unsold packages












     RAFFLES, PARTIES & FIX PRICED
Selling additional items is a breeze.

Raffle tickets
Sign-up parties
Mystery boxes
Wine Pulls
Merchandise
Beverage Tickets















     Donor Management
Track donations, manage communications and acknowledge your auction donors.

Generate auction solicitation requests
Quickly view all donor contributions
Create custom  post-event donor thanks yous
Send email donation reciepts












     SOCIAL MEDIA
Expand your reach beyond the ballroom, with social media functionality.

Share your Facebook and Twitter feeds
Live tweet your event with Twitter Scoreboard
Allow donors to share silent auction pacakges















     PAPER AUCTIONS
BidPal can assist with auctions that may be better suited for paper bid sheets.

Generate paper bid sheets
Print package tent cards
Track winning bids, sold items and donations
Email or print receipts
Manage outstanding payments












     MOBILE APP
Reach your donors with the convenience of our mobile app to further engage your donors.

Send push notifications to donors throughout the year
Review receipts from past events
Track charitable giving from all sources
Stay up to date with current charitable news
Quickly access open mobile bidding events















VIEW SOFTWARE FEATURES (PDF DOWNLOAD)














  






























  



























  










Live Donation Appeal





				Build the excitement of your live donation appeal into an avalanche of giving by allowing your guests to contribute using their cell phones. Results are calculated and displayed in real-time, giving your nonprofit unique opportunities to exceed your goals.			




				Want to try it out? Text DONATE to BIDPAL to make a mock donation. Don’t worry. Your card won’t be charged. 








 














  













Scoreboard





BidPal’s customizable scoreboards provide your event attendees real-time status updates on current bids, incentivizing them to bid more and make sure they go home a winner.





				Using BidPal’s Scoreboard with a live donation appeal provides donor recognition as well as a visual of your fundraising.			




				BidPal Scoreboards additionally have the ability to share your guest’s tweets and pictures in real time helping you take your event and mission viral.			













  






























  



























  













				Easy Event Registration, Checkout & Payments			



Smartpay Anywhere® is included with BidPal’s auction software and mobile bidding.  It is PCI certified and compliant and offers seamless payment processing making event registration and checkout a piece of cake.











REGISTRATION





Give event staff easy access to registrant information
Capture additional guest and credit card information
Enter onsite ticket purchases, fixed price items and donations
Communicate table number and seating





 
















CHECKOUT





Instantaneous access to revenue transactions
No synchronization or import required
Split guest bills into multiple payments
Add tax and/or miscellaneous charges
Offer email or paper receipts
Process payments live onsite





 






VIEW MOBILE BIDDING PACKAGES & PRICING













  






























  











				OFFERING BEST IN CLASS GUIDANCE & INSIGHTS			



DATABASE INTEGRATION
SUPPORT
REPORTING & ANALYTICS










We recognize the importance of maintaining a robust donor database, which is why BidPal’s fundraising software allows you to effortlessly move data between our software and the leading donor databases.
If you use Salesforce to maintain your records, BidPal Connect our Salesforce App provides you the convenience of moving data back and forth with just a few mouse clicks.











The BidPal team of more than 250 fundraising professionals and technologists is ready to help you take your fundraising to the next level.
From our Account Managers to our state-of-the art Support to our Onsite Event Staff we have your back.



MEET OUR TEAM












BidPal’s fundraising software takes the thousands of data points collected before, during and after your event and converts them into actionable items to help you strengthen your mission.
You're in control of your data!  Everything that is stored in BidPal can easily be exported in multiple formats (CSV, PDF, DOC) for additional external analysis.



