      Event Fundraising Software A comprehensive web based event management solution for any type of fundraising event.    





  










				Not all event fundraising software is created equal			




				Managing a fundraising event is challenging for even the most seasoned event planning team.  Be the office hero.  Let BidPal’s event fundraising software simplify your work.			












Event Mgmt







Ticketing







Registration & Check-Out







Payments







