Versatile Event Fundraising Software




BidPal’s robust event fundraising software is designed to help ease the administrative burden and save time when managing event fundraising campaigns.  Its simple yet versatile nature makes it the perfect event management tool for any type of fundraising event.





Try BidPal event fundraising software at your next:

Gala
Golf Outing
Luncheon
Community Event
Class / Seminar
Sporting Event














































Event Promotion & Donor Engagement




BidPal offers custom event websites that are easy to use and set up via our event fundraising software.  They provide:

BRAND AWARENESS
EVENT PROMOTION
