				Designed for Fundraisers			












     Ticketing
Sell tickets and manage RSVPs online to save you and your guests time.

Customize your ticket packages for donors & sponsors
Use coupon codes to offer discounts or incentives
Include VIP, raffle tickets, and party passes
Allow attendees the option to make seating requests and provide guest names
Track guest dietary restrictions
Accept additional donations during ticket purchase












     UNLIMITED EVENTS
Why pay for one event when you can manage multiple events with BidPal for the same price?

Manage an unlimited number of annual events
Easy access to all event data
Copy event set-up from a previous event with one click
Analyze year-over-year event stats















     TABLES & SEATING
Managing table assignments and seating is intuitive and simple with BidPal.

Quickly determine guest count at each table
Assign guests to tables based on requests
Group tables by captain or sponsor
Determine VIP seating












     SOCIAL MEDIA
Expand your reach beyond the ballroom, with social media functionality:

Share Facebook and Twitter feeds via your BidPal event website
Live tweet your event with our customizable Twitter Scoreboard
Provide donors the opportunity to share donations, ticket purchases and bids















     DONOR MANAGEMENT
Track donations, manage communication and easily acknowledge donors.

View all donor contributions
Generate auction solicitation requests
Create custom post-event donor thank yous
Send email donation reciepts












     AUCTION
Best in class online auction software designed to pair with your event.

Track auction item procurement
Manage item storage locations
Categorize items into packages
Sell raffle tickets and fixed price item














